  <hasValue rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">a favorable attitude toward an idea, situation, person, or group. In the context of psychotherapy and counseling, it is the receptive, nonjudgmental attitude of therapists or counselors, which conveys an implicit respect and regard for their clients as individuals.</hasValue>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

