  <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">apa_definition: a state of extreme awareness and watchfulness directed by one or more members of a group toward the environment, often toward potential threats (e.g., predators, intruders, enemy forces in combat).</rdfs:comment>
